network.param.modules.receipts

Interface IDocument

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IBean
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Document

    public interface IDocument
extends IBean
    An interface represents the Param Document/Receipt.

    This interface IDocument will represents documentID, parent documentID, document type.., IDocument defines below categories of operations:

    • setParentDocument method to set parent document.

    • getParentDocumentID method to get parent document ID.

    • setInward method to set setInward, if its reverse flow.

    • getParentDocumentType method for get the getParentDocumentType.

    • setDocumentID method to set document ID.

    • getInternalID method get the catalogue internal ID

    • setCategories method set parent and child category

    • setInternalID method for set the internal id and document type.

    • setNote method for set document note

    • getNote method for get catalogue blockchain ID

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Jitendra Kumar Balla, ParamNetwork
